lead_paragraph: The appetite for gadgets and gimmicks at the Super Bowl is typically low. Surprising the other team with a safety blitz or deep pass, sure, but the risk of true trickery can often seem too steep with a title on the line.

headline.main: The Super Bowl's Most Memorable Trick Plays
